com.ai

Enum NanoTokens

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NanoTokens>
      • com.ai.NanoTokens
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasPattern, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NanoTokens>

    public enum NanoTokens
extends java.lang.Enum<NanoTokens>
implements HasPattern
    Token set for the NanoC scripting Language. Each index of this enum represents a specific terminal of the NanoC grammer. There is a string for each enum type that can be retrieved by the getPattern() method.
    Author:
    Martin Tice
